{"tid":93649,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［召喚行山撚同環保撚］絲帶應否拆除","createTime":"2017-01-24T14:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T11:41:12.000Z","uid":12623,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f4565a3c67ada3f40ef8f6854922c106ebfb59f","tid":93649,"uid":12623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:47:58.000Z","msg":"近排行山界經常發起「上山執垃圾」活動，好多人都效法去上山清理垃圾，更有人喺 Facebook 成立群組，鼓勵啲人上山執下垃圾，為環境出一分力<br />\n<br />\n宜家陸陸續續有好多人鐘意行山／上山打卡，垃圾量有增無減，有賴市民上山清理垃圾，山頭先可以得到一時嘅寧靜<br />\n<br />\n不過問題就嚟，開始有人連山上嘅絲帶都當係垃圾咁一併處理<br />\n<br />\n「熟知」（小弟只係行過10幾次山，識少少扮代表，有錯就細力屌）<br />\n山頭絲帶嘅人都會知道絲帶嘅作用，絲帶係用嚟標示俾山友知條路線，有啲唔係官方嘅路線大多需要依靠絲帶引路，可想而知，絲帶並唔係「垃圾」<br />\n<br />\n不過絲帶又唔會係普見嗰隻嘅絲帶，會有膠帶丶布丶尼龍繩丶甚至係有圖案嘅膠紙(引用山系。清道夫 Wild Sweeper 嘅一則轉貼），所以唔排除會令到生態環境造成傷害<br />\n<br />\n但係，由於絲帶有佢套系統，就係一條路線都會有指定嘅絲帶標示住，所以例如同一個分叉位會可能出現多隻顏色嘅絲帶出現<br />\n<br />\n我之前都嘗試過同環保撚討論過應唔應該拆絲，我嘅立場係唔鼓勵拆，不過唔夠人講就走場了事⋯<br />\n<br />\n想知大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry 有啲長"},{"pid":"9331ef46419be765084c9d32a3c099b5cd6c7634","tid":93649,"uid":12623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:50:40.000Z","msg":"推到有人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2726c017a6cc27874a80b96a2fa6e998ccae38ee","tid":93649,"uid":12623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49deaccecd26b12ffcc382daccf1bcdf68a40de","tid":93649,"uid":8493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:52:45.000Z","msg":"如果要保護環境,其實就唔應該行山<br />\n<br />\n踩到草地已經係破壞, 亦會令土壤變硬,吋草不生<br />\n<br />\n環保撚係咪應該發起不行山運動呢？"},{"pid":"152794deb0ea4ccbd831a830399378c6c3efa14b","tid":93649,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c157b4b55854176a368de5d0367e1dcf52be7b","tid":93649,"uid":60449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95af9f4ccae9a24fdcecc500de6c116e48bd3900","tid":93649,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c66bca241225f67abd00d80ec18f4fdff31cc3","tid":93649,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"我覺得應該拆<br />\n<br />\n然後用另一個方式紀錄路線<br />\n<br />\n利申 <br />\n<br />\n行左廿零次山 <br />\n<br />\n未諗到用咩方式紀錄<br />\n<br />\n淨係由唔破壞嘅前提諗覺得應該拆"},{"pid":"e2ec72163c3a6f2e3f3fa78aa4ef84be1c4c6fe8","tid":93649,"uid":57636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:03:32.000Z","msg":"拆完之後d人爆林亂咁行未重衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c416187ee6ce565ddbc46947960533d73af705","tid":93649,"uid":12623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得應該拆<br />\n<br />\n然後用另一個方式紀錄路線<br />\n<br />\n利申 <br />\n<br />\n行左廿零次山 <br />\n<br />\n未諗到用咩方式紀錄<br />\n<br />\n淨係由唔破壞嘅前提諗覺得應該拆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有次同 friend 試行薄刀刃都要靠絲帶引路<br />\n記憶最深嗰次係玩命大霧行杯靈，都係因為有絲帶先冇賴嘢<br />\n<br />\n我都覺得從環境角度睇係應該要拆<br />\n問題係現時一拆，你就要諗埋用乜方法代替絲帶<br />\n最慘係，宜家拆哂又唔用其他方法標示翻條路<br />\n又或者係，有機會前一部分拆哂，後部分仲留喺度，咁一定出事㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e4dfed3b3ac434ae031d38982b2852c974a08d","tid":93649,"uid":12623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拆完之後d人爆林亂咁行未重衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蕩失路，行入結界都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489f2528bf9bbed03acccf78bfa140fbe80dd912","tid":93649,"uid":43422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:11:23.000Z","msg":"絲帶真係幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGPS實際都可能唔準，但絲帶所俾到既信心真係無得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗少少尼龍、膠帶又唔會話真係破壞到本地生態到無可挽救既地步掛<br />\n同埋平時見到都綁得幾實，無必要連一條膠帶都容納唔到掛<br />\n咁當然，如果可以全部替換為絲帶或者其他環保物料就最好"},{"pid":"98ee5d6e229be1b61acf8f208c7bbe74dfdc6f43","tid":93649,"uid":12623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:15:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果要保護環境,其實就唔應該行山<br />\n<br />\n踩到草地已經係破壞, 亦會令土壤變硬,吋草不生<br />\n<br />\n環保撚係咪應該發起不行山運動呢？</blockquote><br />\n唔知點應你好，利申唔是環保撚<br />\n不過行山幾好玩<br />\n或者站喺環保角度，行山係另一種身教的保護環境方式<br />\n不過呢排就畀班MK仔女打卡污染咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced8fa8936ea71d8b1a6919f0210b247745b4397","tid":93649,"uid":58954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"緊係唔拆啦 <br />\n有好多隱蔽小徑都係靠絲帶先認到<br />\n有絲帶就有路跟本係約定俗成<br />\n啲環保撚係到亂咁拆好多路會好難搵返<br />\n利伸 支持環保撚上山執其他垃圾 但絲帶一定唔好搞"},{"pid":"fea902f0d05834714202e6980fd90b883df478f8","tid":93649,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"其實絲帶你唔理佢，佢基本上唔會跌落黎，唔綁死又唔會傷樹<br />\n對環境基本上無影響<br />\n無左絲帶，對紙質地圖需求會否上升？<br />\n無左絲帶，會否令更多人迷路？<br />\n其實真正行山撚係唔會留低垃圾<br />\n俾起執垃圾，我更覺得應該推廣leave no trace。首先第一步係減少山上垃圾桶數量"},{"pid":"e0a473cd7fb0b555ba6f75a66b3b972f064bc302","tid":93649,"uid":12623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:20:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲帶真係幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGPS實際都可能唔準，但絲帶所俾到既信心真係無得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗少少尼龍、膠帶又唔會話真係破壞到本地生態到無可挽救既地步掛<br />\n同埋平時見到都綁得幾實，無必要連一條膠帶都容納唔到掛<br />\n咁當然，如果可以全部替換為絲帶或者其他環保物料就最好</blockquote><br />\n啲人話絲帶會整死啲植物，我冇 Bio 常識就唔知點應佢啦<br />\n不過之前我都有同人討論過，有人建議可唔可以用其他環保物料取代<br />\n問題係好難唔需要大量時間物資處理，其一係唔同路線有指定嘅顏色同絲帶標示住，其二係有啲秒道好撚危險，萬一有傷亡就GG啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c04eca07bc1978cba02f24431bdc19818886fe7","tid":93649,"uid":12623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf147f380f884947ef6cffc6ed1ed94a21ef51a","tid":93649,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"樓主高質"},{"pid":"a6f4051386855c0a91ed24112c4602af8ef123e3","tid":93649,"uid":9298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:25:29.000Z","msg":"絲帶你信心座標, 無傷大雅, 同時亦已存在多年, 唔見得樹林受到任何程度既傷害, 但就幫左無數既信念不足既人士, 有人講話gps 一樣可以幫手手睇路, 但事實係係荒山野嶺密林既地方行錯一度已經行左唔知去邊, 收手啦偽環保撚"},{"pid":"83c23f12c0b59bb25d92735ec0f7c933a0e077bc","tid":93649,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主高質</blockquote><br />\naggar"},{"pid":"ad7e3ad492346abd68817346364c241c8867c177","tid":93649,"uid":61989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:27:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45ed0a5e5728201631cd76949753b3170d193508","tid":93649,"uid":12623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1215292325225011/permalink/1237950696292507/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1215292325225011%2Fpermalink%2F1237950696292507%2F&d=krEhaDft%2FKezr%2FJ1sG2KPIscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=446b8cf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/121529232522501